title: Drawing, "Design for Tapestry with Cats and Fish"
creditline: Gift of Mr. Eric and Mrs. Sylvia Elsesser, The Trude Guermonprez Archives
description: Traced sketch of seated cat with two kittens framed on left by tulips and on right by a fish with fish bones curving around cat's feet.
